    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款受“抓老 maid”启发的 2-8 人卡牌游戏。你的目标是诱使对手抽到会伤害自己的卡牌，并避开那些能帮助他们的卡牌。你可以通过与对手交流，或者像现实中一样，将手中的卡牌稍微旋转或移动位置，从而引导对手做出错误的选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/7c961d0b59b795b75b25c93a7e3f525b.poster.avif?t=1760393112\" width=720 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/7c961d0b59b795b75b25c93a7e3f525b.webm?t=1760393112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/7c961d0b59b795b75b25c93a7e3f525b.mp4?t=1760393112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/e8b57ffce6fbd478e5cc29e31a1754e8.webp?t=1760393112\" width=720 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为持牌者，你的目标是让当前的抽牌者从你的手牌中抽到错误的卡牌。你可以运用一些简单的小技巧，比如旋转卡牌，或者让某张卡牌的位置高于或低于其他卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/1a5425687c90f499c77f6b4f98856080.webp?t=1760393112\" width=720 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每回合会从仍然存活的持牌者中选出一位成为抽牌者。你处于危险中，必须避免被任何持牌者诱骗而抽到会对你造成伤害的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300300/extras/5f65d686735de6569468b9d79c14f80b.webp?t=1760393112\" width=720 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义的玩法： </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调整牌堆中每种卡牌的数量</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置每位玩家的生命值</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及更多选项</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用服务器浏览器轻松找到开放大厅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的 Steam 头像作为角色形象</p></li></ul>",
